   603Ôćĺ    /**
   604Ôćĺ    An implementation of `Value` based on a library called `value_bag`.
   605Ôćĺ
   606Ôćĺ    `value_bag` was written specifically for use in `log`'s value, but was split out when it outgrew
   607Ôćĺ    the codebase here. It's a general-purpose type-erasure library that handles mapping between
   608Ôćĺ    more fully-featured serialization frameworks.
